&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Your friends would define you as the “getting things done” type;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The Agile philosophy is your lifestyle;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;We won’t have to tell you anything about mobile development for Android. You’ll be the one teaching us your best practices;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;An additional bonus for us would be your experience with testing frameworks (JUnit, Mockito, Espresso), scripting languages (Gradle, Groovy, Python), and/or Jenkins.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Job&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;At Backbase, we don’t just deliver software – we redefine how people manage their finances. We are looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Senior AI Applied Software Engineer &lt;/strong&gt;to join our R&amp;amp;D department in Kraków. You will join the team which sits at the core of Backbase platform: Entitlements. Handling complex problems related to Access Control, Approvals and Limits.&lt;br&gt;By joining our team, you won’t just write code; you will design systems that impact millions of users across over 100 financial institutions worldwide.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Meet the Job&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;As a Senior AI Applied Software Engineer&amp;nbsp; you are a technical cornerstone of your squad. You will design and deliver complex features with minimal guidance, ensuring that both the &quot;engine&quot; (Backend) and the &quot;experience&quot; (Frontend) are performant, secure, and scalable.&lt;/div&gt;
