&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technical Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt; Act as a go-to resource for your team, mentoring junior engineers, conducting critical code reviews, and raising the bar for engineering standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI &amp;amp; Innovation:&lt;/strong&gt; Contribute to the evolution of LLM-based voice assistants and real-time personalization engines using OpenAI and ML models.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security-First Mindset:&lt;/strong&gt; Implement &quot;Entitlements&quot; and fraud prevention services with a focus on non-functional requirements like security, scalability, and resilience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborative Culture:&lt;/strong&gt; Work in a Pod based model, collaborating with Architects, Product Owners, and UX Designers to align technical solutions with business needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
