&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: &lt;/strong&gt;You live in Kraków or nearby area and you are willing to work in a hybrid mode - twice per week from our office.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience:&lt;/strong&gt; You have &lt;strong&gt;5–7+ years&lt;/strong&gt; of professional experience building complex, high-traffic products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Backend Mastery:&lt;/strong&gt; Solid understanding of &lt;strong&gt;Java&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;Spring JPA/Hibernate&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;Maven&lt;/strong&gt;. Experience with &lt;strong&gt;Microservices&lt;/strong&gt; (Netflix OSS is a plus) and Cloud technologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Frontend Expertise:&lt;/strong&gt; Strong skills in &lt;strong&gt;Angular&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;TypeScript&lt;/strong&gt;. You are proficient with &lt;strong&gt;RxJS&lt;/strong&gt; and modern build systems (Webpack, Jenkins). Experience with Vue.js is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;System Design:&lt;/strong&gt; You have a solid grasp of &lt;strong&gt;Enterprise Integration Patterns&lt;/strong&gt; and can design systems that handle complex data flows between services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The &quot;Senior&quot; Edge:&lt;/strong&gt; You don&#39;t just solve tickets; you identify gaps in tooling, reduce technical debt, and optimize CI/CD pipelines to streamline delivery.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communication:&lt;/strong&gt; Excellent English (spoken and written). You can confidently explain technical concepts to non-technical stakeholders and get buy-in for your architectural decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
