&lt;p&gt;The Role&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are seeking a Senior AI applied software Engineer strong backend software engineering experience&lt;/strong&gt; to own the health of our production systems by resolving complex escalations and driving automation. Our core backend relies heavily on Java, Spring Boot, and microservices orchestrated via Kubernetes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, we embrace a T-shaped engineering profile. You will anchor your work in your deep expertise of the Java ecosystem, while utilizing AI tools to operate across the wider tech stack.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Rather than just closing tickets, you will use AI and agentic workflows as force multipliers to optimize our support processes, automate repetitive triage tasks, and permanently resolve underlying system defects. You will serve as a technical authority who mentors peers and raises the bar on how we handle application support in a modern, cloud-native environment.&lt;/p&gt;
