&lt;p&gt;End-to-End Troubleshooting: Take ownership of complex escalations by debugging Java and Spring Boot code, tracing issues through REST APIs, and resolving bottlenecks in our microservices architecture.&lt;br&gt;AI-Driven Automation: Lead the adoption of agentic tooling, LLMs, and AI automation to streamline incident triage, log analysis, and repetitive support workflows as you identify system pain points.&lt;br&gt;Infrastructure Navigation: Monitor, debug, and maintain application stability within a Kubernetes-orchestrated containerized environment.&lt;br&gt;Technical Authority: Act as the highest escalation point and go-to resource for your peers. Review root cause analyses critically and mentor the team on modern, AI-native support practices.&lt;br&gt;Strategic Problem Solving: Identify trends in system failures, lead cross-system investigations, and plan major code refactoring or automation initiatives to prevent recurrence.&lt;br&gt;Quality Excellence: Balance rapid incident response speeds with long-term system maintainability, championing performance and reliability standards.&lt;/p&gt;
