&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Backbase:&lt;/strong&gt; Backbase is the leading AI-powered banking platform that is used by financial institutions worldwide to create seamless digital experiences. As a Senior Database Engineer in our Retail department, you&#39;ll be instrumental in optimizing the core data infrastructure that powers these experiences for millions of users, directly contributing to our mission of reinventing banking. Join our team at Backbase, one of the LinkedIn Top Companies of 2023 in the Netherlands, known for our great work environment and opportunities for career growth. We&#39;re committed to fostering a culture of collaboration, innovation, and growth, where you&#39;ll work with some of the brightest and most talented people in the industry to help shape the future of digital banking.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The job in short:&lt;/strong&gt; Are you a performance enthusiast with a deep understanding of databases, ready to be the ultimate database authority within Backbase? As a Senior Database Engineer (also known as a Senior Performance Engineer or DBA), you&#39;ll diagnose and resolve complex database performance issues, ensuring our digital banking platform operates at peak efficiency for our global customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Meet the job:&lt;/strong&gt; Database performance engineers are a cornerstone of Backbase technology. You&#39;ll provide invaluable guidance to our development teams (tribes and squads) in their approach to databases and data design, ensuring our microservices deliver optimum performance. You&#39;ll analyze and interpret large volumes of performance data to characterize application behavior while proactively scanning for potential problems. Once an issue or bottleneck is identified, you&#39;ll build simulations to test your findings, and upon confirmation, you&#39;ll clearly explain it to Technical Architects and guide them towards a solution. We believe in having the guts to push limits and break barriers to make things happen, continuously learning and reinventing ourselves for maximum impact, never giving up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your duties will include:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Explaining complex findings to a variety of technical audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Testing our Proof-of-Concept (PoC) products to ensure they achieve our ambitious goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensuring overall software quality, scalability, and performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working closely with our cloud solutions team on their Minimum Viable Product (MVP) and launch.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Acting as a consultant to our internal development teams and educating them on performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How about you?&lt;/strong&gt; Looking for a journey instead of a job? Then let’s talk! We are THE pioneers in banking tech. As a Senior Database Engineer at Backbase, your role expands beyond the day-to-day operations of engineering. If you’re a curious go-getter with a passion for working with people and challenging your own skill set, then this is for you. We are creators, with a customer-centric mindset that loves what they do and brings fun to any challenge. Together we kick ass, have fun and feel proud when our vision is delivered. The next day - we wake up and raise the bar a little higher.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To really tackle this role, we believe you’ll need:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid experience with large (100TB+), highly available, and high-transaction databases, with MySQL being a must-have (Oracle or MSSQL is a plus).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with Cloud databases, either AWS or Azure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep knowledge about database fundamentals and architectures, alongside SQL code performance review and optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with standard edition tools for performance measurement, analysis, and optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with developing tools and methodology for is

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Job in Short&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Delivery Manager, you will be responsible for supervising the best-in-class delivery service with some of the top customers. You will be required to carefully steer and monitor performance across these projects and maintain customer success and satisfaction while ensuring that our relationship with them continues to grow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Meet the Job&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Backbase is a fintech company that provides a software platform to help banks and credit unions modernize their digital services. Instead of building their own complex apps from scratch, these financial institutions use the Backbase Engagement Banking Platform to quickly create a seamless, customer-centric digital experience for their users. In essence, Backbase gives banks the tools to build a modern, user-friendly digital facade that sits on top of their older, legacy core systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role of a Delivery Manager, involves overseeing the delivery process of projects to ensure they meet quality standards and customer expectations. The Delivery Manager is primarily involved in the Setup phase of a project, supporting and executing activities such as planning, coordinating with various teams, and facilitating workshops like the CXO Workshops. They work closely with the Project Manager, Business Analyst, Solution Architect, and Engineering Manager, forming part of the core team responsible for successful project execution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1071&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How about You&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have 10+ years experience in leading complex software delivery projects;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You can demonstrate experience in the banking/financial services sector(s);&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience with senior level stakeholder management in an international environment;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience in an agile environment, experience with SDLC, SCRUM, and LEAN;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have experience in distributed and remote agile delivery;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You enjoy visiting customers onsite and don&#39;t shy away to travel frequently;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have excellent oral and written communication skills in Arabic and English;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are based in Lebanon or Jordan.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1&quot; data-local-id=&quot;d0d29c11c3d5&quot;&gt;As a &lt;strong data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Senior Delivery Manager&lt;/strong&gt;, you are the independent driver of success for large and complex projects, ensuring customer needs are met from the initial planning phase through to a triumphant go-live.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;204&quot; data-local-id=&quot;1a98ab9ee77e&quot;&gt;You are fully accountable for the final result, diligently managing the entire project lifecycle, including budget, risk, and scope. You uphold theBackbase way of working, translating process efficiency into a clear, practical reality for both the delivery team and the customer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;485&quot; data-local-id=&quot;4a7c8b6678bf&quot;&gt;You create a seamless environment where every single player, both on the customer and Backbase side, understands their role and is empowered to excel. While you maintain oversight on deadlines and key dates, you take care of three main areas; &lt;br&gt;You ensure that&amp;nbsp; the &lt;span data-highlighted=&quot;true&quot; data-vc=&quot;highlighted-text&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;_kqswh2mm&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;_5pioz8co _189e1dm9 _1il9buyh _19lc184f _d0altlke&quot; data-testid=&quot;definition-highlighter&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; lead secures necessary sign-offs (BSDs), runs a crystal clear jira admin with one source of truth.&lt;br&gt;You ensure that the Engineering Manager with his team focus on delivering the &lt;span data-highlighted=&quot;true&quot; data-vc=&quot;highlighted-text&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;_kqswh2mm&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;_5pioz8co _189e1dm9 _1il9buyh _19lc184f _d0altlke&quot; data-testid=&quot;definition-highlighter&quot;&gt;BSD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;’s.&lt;br&gt;You control the customer on scope and agreements made to deliver items from their end.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-renderer-start-pos=&quot;1025&quot; data-local-id=&quot;55cc4114441b&quot;&gt;Fundamentally, your role is that of a powerful facilitator. You handle the full spectrum of project administration, from governance, detailed reporting, and meeting setup (including Steering Committees) to intricate internal and external stakeholder management, budget tracking, payments, and team planning. You artfully remove every possible distraction, ensuring the team can work with laser focus on their tasks, maintaining a light touch that keeps you informed without interrupting their flow. As a forward-thinking leader, you also know how to leverage AI to enhance and streamline your project management activities.&lt;/p&gt;
